choices.text: the discovery and exploitation of the Canal. If brought back to the time of Columbus, Panama would be nothing but a picturesque area of beaches, beautiful tropical Panamanian people, and natural resources. If you are a visitor to our beautiful beaches in Las Lajas, Panama, El Valle de Anton, Mira Flores, Cabuya, and other areas in Panama, be reminded of these scenes and of much contact with indigenous people such as Sangalos, Indians, and Embera. Also, Victor Valdes and I were remarkable full-time high school teachers and active section leaders in choirs in the Republic of Panama.
